    "skills": [
        {
            "name": "鸣雷",
            "icon": "/public/images/character/skillicon/icon_combo_skill_ikut_01.png",
            "description": "当有敌人进入<#ba.conduct>导电</>状态或<#ba.conduct>导电</>状态被<#ba.consume>消耗</>后可以发动。\n瞬闪至敌人身边进行多次斩击，造成<@ba.pd>物理伤害</>，并恢复一定技力。",
            "groupType": "ComboSkill",
            "skillIds": [
                "chr_0007_ikut_combo_skill"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "循迹逐猎",
            "icon": "/public/images/character/skillicon/icon_attack_sword.png",
            "description": "普通攻击：\n对敌人进行至多5段攻击，造成<@ba.pd>物理伤害</>。作为主控干员时，<#ba.lastcombo>重击</>会造成<@ba.poise>{poise:0}</>点失衡。\n\n下落攻击：\n处于空中时使用普通攻击，会下落并攻击附近敌人，造成<@ba.pd>物理伤害</>。\n\n处决攻击：\n附近有敌人处于失衡状态时使用普通攻击，将处决该敌人，造成大量<@ba.pd>物理伤害</>并恢复一定技力。",
            "groupType": "NormalAttack",
            "skillIds": [
                "chr_0007_ikut_attack1",
                "chr_0007_ikut_attack2",
                "chr_0007_ikut_attack3",
                "chr_0007_ikut_attack4",
                "chr_0007_ikut_attack5",
                "chr_0007_ikut_power_attack",
                "chr_0007_ikut_plunging_attack_end"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "疾风迅雷",
            "icon": "/public/images/character/skillicon/icon_skill_ikut_01.png",
            "description": "瞬闪至敌人身边进行2次斩击，造成少量<@ba.pd>物理伤害</>。若敌人处于<#ba.conduct>导电</>状态，<#ba.consume>消耗</>其<#ba.conduct>导电</>状态并追加一次攻击，造成<@ba.pulse>电磁伤害</>，然后恢复一定技力。",
            "groupType": "NormalSkill",
            "skillIds": [
                "chr_0007_ikut_normal_skill"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "轰雷掣电",
            "icon": "/public/images/character/skillicon/icon_ultimate_skill_ikut_01.png",
            "description": "用电弧包裹自身后向前方冲刺一段距离，对路径上的敌人造成<@ba.pulse>电磁伤害</>并施加<#ba.pulseinflict>电磁附着</>。一段时间后，引爆留下的电弧，再次造成<@ba.pulse>电磁伤害</>，若敌人处于<#ba.pulseinflict>电磁附着</>状态，则会<#ba.consume>消耗</>其<#ba.pulseinflict>电磁附着</>并强制施加<#ba.conduct>导电</>。",
            "groupType": "UltimateSkill",
            "skillIds": [
                "chr_0007_ikut_ultimate_skill"
            ]
        }
    ],
